lines.text:
[after Repairman #1 takes advantage of her changing clothes around him]
But I don't even know you. I don't even know your name...

[after he takes her from behind thinking it's his wife]
Pa! I didn't know it was you. My God.
Yeah, it did. It felt wonderful. I love this, I love fucking my daughter! Oh, when I tell the old lady she's through!
